snippet.title: CYBRID (VR Game) - Available now on Steam | Trailer
snippet.description:
CYBRID is the action-rhythm VR Game Available now on Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1636850/CYBRID/

CYBRID is the action-rhythm VR of the Cyber Future! Swords and Pistols are in your hands. Slash and Shoot! Don't let this stop you! Run, dodge, and jump among the neon lights of the city to a powerful soundtrack!

Shada Games
